fm: vector<vector<int>> reconstructQueue(vector<vector<int>> &people) {         vector<vector<int>> res;         unordered_map<int, vector<int>> people_map;         vector<int> people_set;         for (auto &p:people) {             if (people_map.find(p[0]) == people_map.end())                 people_set.push_back(p[0]);             people_map[p[0]].push_back(p[1]);         }         sort(people_set.begin(), people_set.end());         for (auto p = people_set.rbegin(); p < people_set.rend(); ++p) {             sort(people_map[*p].begin(), people_map[*p].end());             for (int j = 0; j < people_map[*p].size(); ++j)                 res.insert(res.begin() + people_map[*p][j],                            vector<int>{*p, people_map[*p][j]});         }         return res;     }

fm: int longestPalindrome(string s) {         unordered_map<char, int> m;         int num = 0, odd = 0;         for (auto c:s)             ++m[c];         for (auto iter:m) {             num += 2 * (iter.second / 2);             if (odd == 0)                 odd = iter.second % 2;         }         return num + odd;     }

fm: int numberOfArithmeticSlices(vector<int> &A) {         int size = A.size();         if (size <= 2) return 0;         int len = 0, num = 0;         for (int i = 1; i < size - 1; ++i) {             if (A[i] - A[i - 1] == A[i + 1] - A[i])                 ++len;             else {                 num += len * (len + 1) / 2;                 len = 0;             }         }         if (len)             num += len * (len + 1) / 2;         return num;     }

fm: int thirdMax(vector<int> &nums) {         set<int> se;         for (auto n:nums)             se.insert(n);         return se.size() >= 3 ? *(--(--(--se.end()))) : *(--se.end());     }
